'''''Firewind''''' was a [[Victory-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Victory''-class Star Destroyer]] that served in the [[Death Squadron/Legends|Death Squadron]].

==History==
During the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]], it was not in its assigned position when the assault began. This was due to [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Kendal Ozzel/Legends|Ozzel]] ordering the fleet to drop out of hyperspace close to [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]] rather than a farther distance away.

